{"tid":2437847,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"創辦18年來首次  改革派贏深藍會長 西醫工會變天","createTime":"2021-03-08T06:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T08:06:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dd38a08c20d33dca7edfd293db8b1ccea3689477","tid":2437847,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:47:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/V66PBRQIVFBUJIRDBBEV2SVDN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FV66PBRQIVFBUJIRDBBEV2SVDN4%2F&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058vdVh5kQGr0UM1CkPSjmotI%3D&h=3a9a59a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FV66PBRQIVFBUJIRDBBEV2SVDN4%2F&h=c7297d54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/V66PBRQIVFBUJIRDBBEV2SVDN4/</a><br />\n<br />\n創辦18年來首次 <br />\n改革派贏深藍會長 西醫工會變天<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港西醫工會變天。西醫工會選舉一波三折，需兩度押後投票，昨日終有結果。矢言要改革工會的前副會長梁漢輝以32票之差，擊敗被指立場深藍、創會18年的歷任會長楊超發，成功當選為會長。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：開明醫護三連勝 破建制壟斷<br />\n<br />\n西醫工會擁有逾1,500名會員，幹事會共有17名成員，是次有九個職位改選，包。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AhIYJ0CiER8vlghcn8Vt_Evn9Sw=/510x333/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VB3XFZXM3FG3FORWS7AQBWPN3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAhIYJ0CiER8vlghcn8Vt_Evn9Sw%3D%2F510x333%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVB3XFZXM3FG3FORWS7AQBWPN3U.jpg&h=4b26fc67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■矢言要改革西醫工會的梁漢輝昨當選會長，與新任秘書胡志和及司庫陸偉亮握拳興奮慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n選前因調查工會賬目、被時任會長楊超發革除職務的前副會長梁漢輝在今次選舉取得256票，楊超發獲224票，梁以32票。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n梁表示經過艱難過程才當選會長，自言一年前已發現楊管理有問題，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-9VwHwVL0_xuTIO4CVEgyZxpVMQ=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E7US3AXZTZGRJHZJFMGIQ5YANY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-9VwHwVL0_xuTIO4CVEgyZxpVMQ%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE7US3AXZTZGRJHZJFMGIQ5YANY.jpg&h=321acbd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■落選的創會會長楊超發一臉落寞離開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n司庫：上任着手查賬目<br />\n<br />\n梁又希望工會能重回正軌，稱當選後首要工作是團結工會及幹事會；工會作為政府諮詢機構，未來亦會跟進各項政策，包括政府。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n成功競逐連任的義務司庫陸偉亮則指，會成立委員會處理工會問題，包括。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n楊在選舉完結後未有回應任何提問，一臉落寞離開。楊擔任西醫工會會。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n楊亦在2016年成立「反港獨西醫前線」，以「反港獨、反壟斷、只對。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3_xkFtb3zY-AOZSdmsQwCHredNw=/466x658/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GATBARPZUNCXVAKJJID7XYGFKI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3_xkFtb3zY-AOZSdmsQwCHredNw%3D%2F466x658%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGATBARPZUNCXVAKJJID7XYGFKI.gif&h=1ee305c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c82ae8bf729e732d3f7877ad77508b46d07deed7","tid":2437847,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"反港獨西醫前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65dedee8df6a27a235380a2ce1fd0de4a54fcc7c","tid":2437847,"uid":128261,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c82ae8bf729e732d3f7877ad77508b46d07deed7","tid":2437847,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"反港獨西醫前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:26:55.000Z","msg":"絕大多數醫生又唔做支那人生意，又唔受經濟週期影響，唔明佢地點解咁撚奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj